Earthquake Anniversary *** ARCHIVE

Haiti marks the 10th anniversary of a devastating 2010 earthquake which killed thousands on 12 January. PORT-AU-PRINCE, HAITI | 12 JANUARY 2020 AP will offer the following facilities in Port-au-Prince: — Live stand-up positions in key locations — Multi-format tape playout — International delivery via AP’s satellite and fibre networks AP BOOKINGS LONDON +44 (0)20 7482 7580 / 7590 bookings@ap.org www.ap.org/live-and-location-services/ Follow us: @AP_GMS
